               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18590131-name-327" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18590131-name-327" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18590131-name-327" type="surname" value="WAITES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18590131-name-327" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH WAITES</persName>
                  </hi> I am a draper of High-street, Woolwich—on Thursday, 20th January about 3 o'clock in the afternoon, I had four pairs of trowsers hanging to a piece of tape outside my shop—I missed one pair about 5 o'clock; about half-past 7 I heard a wrench, ran to the door, and missed another pair—they were worth 7<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. or 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. a pair.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
